---

---

<section
    class="med-section med-section-local"
>
    <div class="med-container">
        <div class="med-grid">
            <div class="med-info-column">
                <span
                    class="med-tag med-tag-local"
                    >La Ciencia Muerta</span
                >
                <h2 class="med-title med-title-local">
                    El Mapa del Alma
                </h2>

                <p class="med-description med-description-local">
                    En el siglo XIX, creímos que podíamos medir la personalidad con un calibre. Si
                    tenías un bulto aquí, eras un genio. Si lo tenías allá, eras un criminal.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="med-card med-card-local"
                >
                    <h3 class="med-card-title med-card-title-local">Frenología</h3>
                    <p class="med-card-text med-card-text-local">
                        Se usaba para justificar el racismo, decidir matrimonios y contratar
                        empleados. Era "ciencia" aceptada. Se medía el cráneo para juzgar el
                        contenido.
                    </p>
                    <p class="med-card-note med-card-note-local">
                        Hoy sabemos que es una pseudociencia absurda. Pero nos recuerda el peligro
                        de medir lo que queremos ver, no lo que hay.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="med-visual-column">
                <div class="med-visual-sizer">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" class="med-w-full med-h-full">
                        <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="scanGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#fdba74" stop-opacity="0"></stop>
                                <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#fdba74" stop-opacity="1"></stop>
                                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#fdba74" stop-opacity="0"></stop>
                            </linearGradient>
                        </defs>

                        <g stroke="#57534e" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round">
                            {
                                Array.from({ length: 40 }).map((_, i) => {
                                    const y = 50 + i * 8;

                                    let width = 0;
                                    let startX = 200;

                                    if (i < 15) {
                                        width = 100 + Math.sin(i * 0.5) * 20;
                                        startX = 150;
                                    } else if (i < 25) {
                                        width = 110 + Math.cos((i - 15) * 0.5) * 30;
                                        startX = 140;
                                    } else {
                                        width = 60;
                                        startX = 180;
                                    }

                                    return (
                                        <line
                                            x1={startX}
                                            y1={y}
                                            x2={startX + width}
                                            y2={y}
                                            class="med-opacity-30"
                                        />
                                    );
                                })
                            }
                        </g>

                        <rect
                            x="0"
                            y="0"
                            width="400"
                            height="40"
                            fill="url(#scanGradient)"
                            opacity="0.2"
                            class="animate-scan"></rect>
                        <line
                            x1="0"
                            y1="20"
                            x2="400"
                            y2="20"
                            stroke="#fdba74"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            class="animate-scan-line"></line>

                        <g class="animate-pulse-data">
                            <circle cx="200" cy="100" r="3" fill="#fb923c"></circle>
                            <text x="210" y="105" fill="#fb923c" font-size="10"
                                >BENEVOLENCE: 84%</text
                            >
                        </g>

                        <g class="animate-pulse-data" style="animation-delay: 2s">
                            <circle cx="240" cy="80" r="3" fill="#fb923c"></circle>
                            <text x="250" y="85" fill="#fb923c" font-size="10">VENERATION: 12%</text
                            >
                        </g>

                        <g class="animate-pulse-data" style="animation-delay: 4s">
                            <circle cx="160" cy="180" r="3" fill="#fb923c"></circle>
                            <text x="40" y="185" fill="#fb923c" font-size="10"
                                >DESTRUCTIVENESS: 99%</text
                            >
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .med-section-local {
        background-color: #271a12;
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }

    .med-tag-local {
        color: #d6d3d1;
        border-color: #a8a29e;
    }

    .med-title-local {
        color: #f5f5f4;
    }

    .med-description-local {
        color: #d6d3d1;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .med-card-title-local {
        color: #fdba74;
    }

    .med-card-text-local {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }

    .med-card-note-local {
        color: #fb923c;
    }

    .med-card-local {
        background-color: color-mix(in srgb, #451a03 50%, transparent);
        border-color: #78350f;
    }

    @keyframes scan {
        0% {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        100% {
            transform: translateY(360px);
        }
    }
    .animate-scan {
        animation: scan 4s linear infinite;
    }
    .animate-scan-line {
        animation: scan 4s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulseData {
        0%,
        100% {
            opacity: 0;
        }
        10%,
        90% {
            opacity: 1;
        }
    }
    .animate-pulse-data {
        animation: pulseData 4s linear infinite;
    }

    .med-visual-sizer { position: relative; width: 20rem; height: 20rem; }
</style>
